title: Bracelet, mid-19th century
creditline: Gift of the estate and in memory of Robert B. Noyes
description: Hinged bracelet with clasp opening on a slide; shape of a ribbon: green, white, red, dark and light blue and yellow enamel on chased gold, in a one-loop bow on part of the bracelet.

tombstone.epitaph:
Bracelet, mid-19th century.
mid-19th century. Gold, enamel. Gift of the estate and in memory of Robert B. Noyes. 1946-50-5.
